WEBVTT

00:11:58.983 --> 00:12:01.950
admire this mind that he's resented.

00:12:01.950 --> 00:12:03.879
Could it be so simple though?

00:12:03.879 --> 00:12:06.310
What if jealousy really is a matter of geometry,

00:12:06.310 --> 00:12:10.020
just a matter of where we allow ourselves to stand

00:12:10.020 --> 00:12:12.350
in relation to another?

00:12:12.350 --> 00:12:14.221
Well, maybe then we wouldn't have to resent

00:12:14.221 --> 00:12:16.282
somebody's excellence.

00:12:16.282 --> 00:12:19.656
We could align ourselves with it.

00:12:19.656 --> 00:12:21.912
But I like contingency plans.

00:12:21.912 --> 00:12:24.248
So while we wait for that to happen,

00:12:24.248 --> 00:12:26.944
let us remember that we have fiction for consolation.

00:12:26.944 --> 00:12:29.395
Fiction alone demystifies jealousy.

00:12:29.395 --> 00:12:31.478
Fiction alone domesticates it,